{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Last January, my company, Fark.com, was sued"},{"time":4000,"text":"along with Yahoo, MSN, Reddit,"},{"time":7000,"text":"AOL, TechCrunch and others"},{"time":10000,"text":"by a company called Gooseberry Natural Resources."},{"time":13000,"text":"Gooseberry owned a patent"},{"time":15000,"text":"for the creation and distribution"},{"time":17000,"text":"of news releases via email."},{"time":20000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":23000,"text":"Now it may seem kind of strange that such a thing can actually be patented,"},{"time":26000,"text":"but it does happen all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"Take something already being done"},{"time":30000,"text":"and patent it for an emerging technology --"},{"time":32000,"text":"like phone calls on the internet"},{"time":35000,"text":"or video listings for TV shows"},{"time":38000,"text":"or radio but for cellphones,"},{"time":40000,"text":"and so on."},{"time":42000,"text":"The problem with these patents"},{"time":44000,"text":"is that the mechanisms are obscure"},{"time":46000,"text":"and the patent system is dysfunctional,"},{"time":48000,"text":"and as a result, most of these lawsuits end in settlements."},{"time":51000,"text":"And because these settlements are under a non-disclosure agreement,"},{"time":54000,"text":"no one knows what the terms were."},{"time":56000,"text":"And as a result, the patent troll can claim"},{"time":58000,"text":"that they won the case."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61000,"text":"In the case of Gooseberry Natural Resources,"},{"time":63000,"text":"this patent on emailing news releases"},{"time":65000,"text":"had sort of a fatal flaw"},{"time":67000,"text":"as it pertained to myself,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and that was that in the mainstream media world"},{"time":71000,"text":"there is only one definition for news release,"},{"time":74000,"text":"and it turns out that is press release --"},{"time":76000,"text":"as in P.R."},{"time":78000,"text":"Now my company, Fark,"},{"time":80000,"text":"deals with news, ostensibly,"},{"time":82000,"text":"and as a result"},{"time":84000,"text":"we were not in violation of this patent."},{"time":86000,"text":"So case closed, right?"},{"time":88000,"text":"Wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90000,"text":"One of the major problems with patent law is that,"},{"time":92000,"text":"in the case that when you are sued by a patent troll,"},{"time":95000,"text":"the burden of proof that you did not infringe on the patent"},{"time":98000,"text":"is actually on the defendant,"},{"time":100000,"text":"which means you have to prove"},{"time":102000,"text":"that you do not infringe on the patent they're suing you on."},{"time":105000,"text":"And this can take quite a while."},{"time":108000,"text":"You need to know that the average patent troll defense"},{"time":111000,"text":"costs two million dollars"},{"time":113000,"text":"and takes 18 months when you win."},{"time":116000,"text":"That is your best case outcome"},{"time":118000,"text":"when you get sued by a patent troll."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"Now I had hoped to team up with some of these larger companies"},{"time":123000,"text":"in order to defend against this lawsuit,"},{"time":125000,"text":"but one-by-one they settled out of the case,"},{"time":128000,"text":"even though -- and this is important --"},{"time":130000,"text":"none of these companies"},{"time":132000,"text":"infringed on this patent -- not a one of them."},{"time":135000,"text":"And they started settling out."},{"time":137000,"text":"The reason they settled out"},{"time":139000,"text":"is because it's cheaper to settle than to fight the lawsuit --"},{"time":141000,"text":"clearly, two million dollars cheaper in some cases,"},{"time":144000,"text":"and much worse if you actually lose."},{"time":146000,"text":"It would also constitute a massive distraction for management of a company,"},{"time":149000,"text":"especially a small eight-man shop like my company."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152000,"text":"Six months into the lawsuit,"},{"time":154000,"text":"we finally reached the discovery phase."},{"time":156000,"text":"And in discovery phase,"},{"time":158000,"text":"we asked the patent troll to please provide"},{"time":160000,"text":"screenshots of Fark"},{"time":162000,"text":"where the infringement of their patent"},{"time":164000,"text":"was actually occurring."},{"time":166000,"text":"Now perhaps it's because no such screenshots actually existed,"},{"time":170000,"text":"but suddenly Gooseberry wanted to settle."},{"time":172000,"text":"Their attorney:"},{"time":174000,"text":"\"Ah, yes. My company's having a reorganization on our end.\""},{"time":178000,"text":"Never mind the fact"},{"time":180000,"text":"that the address led to a strip mall somewhere in Northern L.A."},{"time":182000,"text":"with no employees."},{"time":184000,"text":"\"And we'd like to go ahead and close this out."},{"time":186000,"text":"So would you mind giving us your best and final offer?\""},{"time":190000,"text":"My response:"},{"time":192000,"text":"\"How about nothing?!\""},{"time":194000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":199000,"text":"We didn't have high hopes for that outcome."},{"time":201000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":203000,"text":"But they settled."},{"time":205000,"text":"No counter offer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"Now, as mentioned before,"},{"time":209000,"text":"one of the reasons I can talk to you about this"},{"time":211000,"text":"is because there's no non-disclosure agreement on this case."},{"time":213000,"text":"Now how did that happen?"},{"time":215000,"text":"Well during the settlement process, when we received our copy, I struck it."},{"time":218000,"text":"My attorney said, \"Nah, no chance of that working.\""},{"time":221000,"text":"It came back signed."},{"time":223000,"text":"Now why? You can call them."},{"time":226000,"text":"They're not under NDA either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228000,"text":"Now what did I learn from this case? Well, three things."},{"time":231000,"text":"First of all, if you can,"},{"time":234000,"text":"don't fight the patent, fight the infringement."},{"time":237000,"text":"Patents are very difficult to overturn."},{"time":239000,"text":"Infringement is a lot easier to disprove."},{"time":242000,"text":"Secondly, make it clear from the beginning"},{"time":244000,"text":"that either you have no money at all"},{"time":246000,"text":"or that you would rather spend money with your attorney fighting the troll"},{"time":250000,"text":"than actually giving them the money."},{"time":252000,"text":"Now the reason this works"},{"time":254000,"text":"is because patent trolls"},{"time":256000,"text":"are paid a percentage of what they're able to recover in settlements."},{"time":259000,"text":"If it becomes clear to them that they cannot recover any money,"},{"time":262000,"text":"they become less interested in pursuing the case."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265000,"text":"Finally, make sure that you can tell them"},{"time":267000,"text":"that you will make this process"},{"time":269000,"text":"as annoying and as painful"},{"time":271000,"text":"and as difficult as possible for them."},{"time":274000,"text":"Now this is a tactic that patent trolls are supposed to use on people"},{"time":276000,"text":"to get their way."},{"time":278000,"text":"It turns out, because they're paid on contingency,"},{"time":280000,"text":"it works really, really well in reverse."},{"time":282000,"text":"Don't forget that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"So what does all this mean?"},{"time":286000,"text":"Well to sum up,"},{"time":288000,"text":"it boils down to one thing:"},{"time":290000,"text":"Don't negotiate with terrorists."},{"time":293000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":298000,"text":"Patent trolls have done more damage to the United States economy"},{"time":301000,"text":"than any domestic or foreign"},{"time":303000,"text":"terrorist organization in history"},{"time":306000,"text":"every year."},{"time":309000,"text":"And what do they do with that money?"},{"time":312000,"text":"They plow it right back into filing more troll lawsuits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316000,"text":"Now this is the point in the Talk"},{"time":318000,"text":"where I'm supposed to come up with some kind of a solution for the patent system."},{"time":321000,"text":"And the problem with that"},{"time":323000,"text":"is that there are two very large industry groups"},{"time":325000,"text":"that have different outcomes in mind"},{"time":327000,"text":"for the patent system."},{"time":329000,"text":"The health care industry"},{"time":331000,"text":"would like stronger protections for inventors."},{"time":333000,"text":"The hi-tech industry"},{"time":335000,"text":"would like stronger protections for producers."},{"time":337000,"text":"And these goals aren't necessarily diametrically opposed, but they are at odds."},{"time":340000,"text":"And as a result, patent trolls can kind of live in the space in between."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"So unfortunately I'm not smart enough"},{"time":346000,"text":"to have a solution for the patent troll problem."},{"time":349000,"text":"However, I did have this idea,"},{"time":352000,"text":"and it was kind of good."},{"time":355000,"text":"And I thought, \"I should patent this.\""},{"time":357000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":360000,"text":"Behold, patent infringement via mobile device --"},{"time":365000,"text":"defined as a computer which is not stationary."},{"time":369000,"text":"My solution: award me this patent"},{"time":371000,"text":"and I will troll them out of existence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}